    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>&quot;I can't wake up... I can't wake up... I can't wake up...&quot;</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The nightmare that never allows waking lasts forever.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You wake up from bed and a girl appears before you. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She calls herself “Entourfe,” a management support android. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The setting is a strange facility, and you will explore the inside of the strange facility with her. ......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>The nightmare lingers. It will drag you to hell itself.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><br>The protagonist, plagued by nightmares<br>He is invited to an underground facility.<br><br>It is a nightmarish place filled with monsters, androids, and members of a bizarre organization.<br><br>Can he overcome the nightmare and escape from it?  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Conundrum: Propositions are presented in sections.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150710/extras/0701520830c2522fc894191716787d31.avif?t=1770506773\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150710/extras_big/0701520830c2522fc894191716787d31.avif?t=1770506773 width=800 height=476 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Tentative answers and answers to the propositions are obtained according to the clarity Level of the search.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150710/extras/d9877d6820ee98607fddfa2ecd04d1a3.avif?t=1770506773\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150710/extras_big/d9877d6820ee98607fddfa2ecd04d1a3.avif?t=1770506773 width=800 height=282 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a text-based adventure game that switches between point-and-click exploration mode and action mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The difficulty level is fairly low, and it's almost a one-way adventure and novel game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Number of endings 3.</p>",
